    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 allowances for Class II comparative hemolysis studies. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions. Relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1) is met at all five evaluated operating points.",
